- Tapping on the edit text adds a new person
- Tapping on the 'plus' button next to contribution opens 'add dish'
- Tapping on 'history' shows the history for this bill split
- Tapping on 'saved' allows you to view previous saved 'totals'
- Need to add a 'save' icon for the total




